==English==
===Etymology===
From [[cellphone]] + [[television]]
===Noun===
'''cellevision'''  (sometimes abbreviated ''[[CV]]'')
#  An electronic communication medium that allows the transmission of real-time or visual images, and often sound to wireless handheld electronic devices. 
#:''I became bored while waiting in the airport so I watched a little '''cellevision'''.''
# Collectively, the programs broadcast via cellevision.
#:''... fifty seven channels and nothing on '''cellevision'''.''